      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This vehicle remains in impeccable showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and reflecting a history of meticulous care. Every surface and mechanical component adheres to the highest criteria of preservation, offering a rare opportunity for the sophisticated buyer to secure a vehicle of peerless quality. An inspection will confirm its status as a benchmark of its model year.",
