    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it stays spotless inside and out. It drives like a total dream and looks even better. If you\u2019re looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message and let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 43000.0,
