    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade 2008 Honda S2000 AP2. This specimen features the high-revving F22C1 inline-four engine, delivering a linear power band and crisp VTEC engagement. The longitudinal rear-wheel-drive layout is paired with a factory Torsen limited-slip differential and a precise close-ratio six-speed manual transmission. Its double-wishbone suspension and rigid X-bone frame remain in factory-spec alignment, offering unparalleled tactile feedback. This is a collector-tier example with all ten original VIN tags present, flawless Grand Prix White paint, and a pristine undercarriage. Meticulously maintained and mechanically absolute.",
